<!-- STORY -->
<section id="story" class="story">
  <div class="wrap grid">
    <div class="imgwrap"><img src="img/heart-scones.jpg" alt="Heart-shaped scones"></div>
    <div>
      <span class="eyebrow">Our story</span>
      <h2>A small kitchen with <em>big flavour.</em></h2>
      <p>Tee's Warm Delights started the way most good things do — at home, at the kitchen table, with flour on the counter and someone asking for "just one more". Today we bake to order for birthdays, tea trays, office mornings, and the quiet moments in between.</p>
      <p>Every scone is rolled by hand. Every cake is layered from scratch. Nothing sits on a shelf — we bake the day you collect, so every bite is still warm.</p>
      <p class="sig">— Tee<small>Owner & head baker</small></p>
      <div class="badges">
        <span class="badge"><span class="d"></span> Small-batch</span>
        <span class="badge"><span class="d"></span> Baked to order</span>
        <span class="badge"><span class="d"></span> Halaal-friendly ingredients</span>
        <span class="badge"><span class="d"></span> No preservatives</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

