      <details class="faq-item" open>
        <summary>How do I place an order?</summary>
        <div class="a">The easiest way is WhatsApp — send us a message with what you'd like, how many, and when you need it for. You can also call or fill in the contact form below. We'll reply with a quote and confirm everything before you pay.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How much notice do you need?</summary>
        <div class="a">For scones, biscuits, and cookies — 24 hours. For cakes, rolls, and larger platters — 48 hours. For big events (50+ people), please give us at least a week so we can plan properly.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Do you deliver?</summary>
        <div class="a">Yes — we deliver locally around Tsakane, Brakpan, and the East Rand for a small fee (depending on distance). Collection is free from our kitchen. Let us know your suburb when you order and we'll sort the rest.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How do I pay?</summary>
        <div class="a">We accept EFT and cash on collection. A small deposit secures larger orders (cakes, platters). Full bank details are shared when we confirm your order.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Can you cater for allergies or halaal?</summary>
        <div class="a">All our ingredients are halaal-friendly. For nut allergies, please let us know up front — we bake with nuts in the kitchen, so we'll advise on what we can safely accommodate.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Do you cater events?</summary>
        <div class="a">Yes — tea tables, dessert tables, office mornings, weddings, and kitchen teas. Send us the date, headcount, and any theme colours and we'll put a proposal together.</div>
      </details>
    </div>
